reviewText: Wish I saw it before visiting the Vatican.
Poorly filmed, colour is not good and several images are out of focus. I actually can't use this with students. There are so many DVDs out there that are so much better.
The video has very poor picture quality. Very jerky. Been there and my pictures were so much better. Don't bother.
I gave this to my husband and we enjoyed it but the quality of the film wasn't what I had hoped for.
